
-------------------(Cmd For Create Project)-----------------------------


*Create New Laravel Project Using Composer

		composer create-project --prefer-dist laravel/laravel your-project-name
		
		
*Create new laravel Project using noraml cmd

		laravel new your-project-name


*Create table using migration 

        php artisan make:migration create_tablename_table


*create model ----> (model name same as tabel name first letter is capital)

        php artisan make:model modelname 

*Create Controller

        php artisan make:controller controllerName
		
					
* create Resource Controller

		php artisan make:controller controllerName --resource
		

*Create Controller Model in one cmd

		php artisan make:model -c-m


*Run Migration 

        php artisan migrate


*Fresh migration 

		php artisan migrate:fresh

*create Request Class

       php artisan make:request RequestName


================================(Cmd For Project alredy Created)======================================  

*Alter Table Concept (Add Column)


		php artisan make:migration add_colname_to_tablename_table --table=table name


*create seeders and add data using seeders

		php artisan make:seeder YourSeederName


#To run a specific seeder:

		php artisan db:seed --class=YourSeederName


#To run all seeders:

		php artisan db:seed




